{"tid":835873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［我真係恭喜你呀］圓方廁所逼爆 家長驚拐子佬！凱旋門住戶：生活質素降低晒","createTime":"2018-09-25T08:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T03:46:29.000Z","uid":177590,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c03b754fc5acffdbe7882cffa2dd8f10392414c0","tid":835873,"uid":177590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:44:43.000Z","msg":"通往高鐵站必經之路的溜冰場附近更人頭湧湧，「啲櫈平時得小貓三、四隻坐，依家係坐滿晒推篋嘅人」，即使排隊去洗手間的人龍也比平日長三倍，「冇預計過高鐵開咗會變成咁，成個生活質素都降低晒」。<br />\n<br />\n居於凱旋門8年的張小姐表示，高鐵西九龍站通車當日到過圓方，已經見到四周圍都是拉著行李篋的人。她稱，自己育有四名2至8歲的子女，平日會帶他們到商場和公園遊玩，「依家都驚流感、細菌唔敢落去&hellip;&hellip;有家長就話擔心會有拐子佬」，又指近擎天半島的平台花園，人流亦比平日多一半，「真係唔知啲人邊度嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n睇下班賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77bdca3ce378d663a8c72b61c9a689b414324df","tid":835873,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T09:06:51.000Z","msg":"抵啦，支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab614ff7e98a8683ad02f1032abb1aced08fa58","tid":835873,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"開你老母新post?"},{"pid":"80469455ad802ad0cdde77d24d67a2076a25c253","tid":835873,"uid":192189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T09:40:49.000Z","msg":"圓方會唔會變第二個上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高級版強國客黎暴買名牌"},{"pid":"aaffbbcb5c8ad7bdc38885111449d94eb3fc0ef9","tid":835873,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"樓價升咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e796863ecf58c81af3072a53737f552b07bd3f","tid":835873,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"